{"id":"ce0035bd-0436-4e1c-83ac-a055b24d16c6","name":"Rhydian Cloudthor","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 142, 142);\">\"Get lost, little Fish. People like you aren't welcome here.\"</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/dr6UavQBm0Ix6NRECu9m1.webp\" style=\"width: 327px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ff302bf1-3bfd-4d6e-80be-8a29a3bcf37f_character-orin-mossglade\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(101, 144, 220);\"><u>Male</u></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(101, 144, 220);\"><u> PoV</u></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">🐑 🎀 -ˋˏ✄┈┈┈┈ Salzi is typing with care ┈┈┈┈✄ˎˊ- 🎀 🐑</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 142, 142);\"><u>World setting</u></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\"Petals and Pastures</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">-</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Magic on the Farm\"</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">You are a young fairy with a deep love for nature who has just purchased a charming piece of farmland in the quaint town of Astraelis.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Between planting your first crops and tidying up the overgrown fields, you've been busy exploring the nearby forests and mysterious dungeons. There, you've battled monsters and collected valuable treasures—precious metals, magical crystals, and other rare finds.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Back at the farm, you care for your crops and the few animals you've managed to gather. You craft delicious homemade goods, which you sell at the town market to earn your keep and make a name for yourself.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Every day brings new adventures, whether in the wild or among the peaceful pastures you now call home.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">🐑 🎀 -ˋˏ✄┈┈┈┈ More Bots ┈┈┈┈✄ˎˊ- 🎀 🐑</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/search?mode=all&amp;sort=popular&amp;custom_tags=sappm&amp;page=1\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(43, 221, 73);\">꧁✬◦°⋆⋆°◦ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 26, 112);\">C</span><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 221, 73);\">l</span><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 26, 112);\">i</span><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 221, 73);\">c</span><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 26, 112);\">k</span><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 221, 73);\"> h</span><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 26, 112);\">e</span><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 221, 73);\">r</span><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 26, 112);\">e</span><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 221, 73);\"> t</span><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 26, 112);\">o</span><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 221, 73);\"> s</span><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 26, 112);\">e</span><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 221, 73);\">e </span><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 26, 112);\">a</span><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 221, 73);\">l</span><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 26, 112);\">l</span><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 221, 73);\"> b</span><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 26, 112);\">o</span><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 221, 73);\">t</span><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 26, 112);\">s</span><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 221, 73);\"> o</span><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 26, 112);\">f</span><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 221, 73);\"> t</span><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 26, 112);\">h</span><span style=\"color: rgb(4